room_title: Escape room "The Diamond Mine" by Amazing Escape Room in New York

room_description: Immersing deeper and deeper underground, you enter an ancient diamond mine. No one's set foot here in years, but the rumors say centuries ago these caves belong to dwarves and were filled with jewels. Can you solve the mystery and escape before you run out of oxygen?
